{
  "stem": "23572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- there was a time we tried to-- we tried to-- my father, I understand, tried to, to get exit visas, to leave.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But really, we had no-- we had nobody in America to get an-- you needed an affidavit of support to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We needed a permit to get to England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, otherwise, we were not that wealthy for us to buy-- I think you could buy yourself a ticket to, to, to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was another place that we were-- people could go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was really no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember, at the end, when it was too late, I think my father was able to get a visa for the-- for Santo Domingo, the Dominican Republic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But by that time, it was, was too late to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You see, nobody wanted Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I experienced that after the war, and-- which we'll come to that, how I really felt again that nobody wanted Jews-- nobody wants Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I felt anti-Semitism in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things, things changed, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- they imposed a lot of restrictions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I mentioned before, you know, you couldn't do this, and you couldn't-- you couldn't go to the stores.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you couldn't-- certainly, you couldn't go to the public-- you couldn't go to the public libraries or the public swimming pools.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember the headlines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember-- there was two, two papers that were prominently displayed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, I didn't have any money to go and buy the paper, you know, even though, in those days, they were a nickel apiece.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you had these-- you had these stands, you know, where-- and that's where the paper were open.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
